configFileTemplateContent:
---
username: ${oxidizedUsername}
password: ${oxidizedPassword}
model: junos
interval: 600
use_syslog: false
debug: false
threads: 30
timeout: 20
retries: 3
prompt: !ruby/regexp /^([\w.@-]+[#>]\s?)$/
rest: 0.0.0.0:8888
vars: {}
groups: {}
pid: "/storage/pid"
input:
  default: ssh, telnet
  debug: false
  ssh:
    secure: false
output:
  default: git
  file:
    directory: "/storage/configs"
  git:
    user: oxidized
    email: oxidized@man.poznan.pl
    repo: "/storage/oxidized.git"
source:
  default: csv
  csv:
    file: "/root/.config/oxidized/router.db"
    delimiter: !ruby/regexp /:/
    map:
      name: 0
      model: 1
model_map:
  cisco: ios
  juniper: junos
